name: FlyingBear S1 0.4 nozzle
machine_start_gcode:
;v2.9.2-20240814;
;wiping nozzle start
M106 P3 S0
M140 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single]
clean_nozzle_position
;wiping nozzle end
;*************preheat nozzle and hotbed for Z_TILT_ADJUST*************
M140 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single]
M104 S130
G1 X110 Y110 F10000 
G4 P200
probe
SET_KINEMATIC_POSITION Z=0 ;Z homing
G1 Z5
M190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single]
Z_TILT_ADJUST 
;*************Z_TILT_ADJUST end*************
M140 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single] ;heat hotbed temp set by user
G1 X5 Y5 F8000 
G28 
G1 X{first_layer_print_min[0]-1.5} Y{min(first_layer_print_min[1] + 100,print_bed_max[0])} F6000 
G1 Z0 F400
M104 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] ;heat nozzle temp set by user
M106 S100 ;close head_nozzle fan
G4 P3000
M106 S255 ;close head_nozzle fan
G4 P3000
M106 S100 ;close head_nozzle fan
;*************PRINT START*************
M109 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] ;heat nozzle temp set by user and wait 
M190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single];heat bed temp set by user and wait 
M106 S0 ;close head_nozzle fan
BED_MESH_CLEAR                                  
BED_MESH_PROFILE LOAD=default   # bedmesh load
G92 E0 ;Reset Extruder
;G1 Z4.0 F200 ;Move Z Axis up
G90 ;absolute position
 ; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; draw line along model
;G92 E0 ;reset extruder
G1 E3 F300 ;extrude filament
G1 X{first_layer_print_min[0]-1.5} Y{min(first_layer_print_min[1] + 100,print_bed_max[0])} F6000 
G1 Z0.22 F600
G1 X{first_layer_print_min[0]-1.5} Y{max(0, first_layer_print_min[1]-1.5)}  F2000 E10
G1 Z0.22 F600
G1 X{min(first_layer_print_min[0] + 60,print_bed_max[0])} F1200 E12
 ; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; ;draw line along model end 
G4 P200
G1 Z2
G92 E0 ;Reset Extruder
CLEAR_PAUSE
;***********model start************
